    "body" : "<p>Many people have mentioned <code>DecimalFormat</code>.  But you can also use <code>printf</code> if you have a recent version of Java:</p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.printf(\"%1.2f\", 3.14159D);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/docs/api/java/util/Formatter.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">See the docs on the Formatter for more information about the printf format string</a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
