    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You may use this quick codes below that changed itself at the end. Add how many zeros as refers to after the point</p>\n\n<pre><code>float y1 = 0.123456789;\nDecimalFormat df = new DecimalFormat(\"#.00\");  \ny1 = Float.valueOf(df.format(y1));\n</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>The variable y1 was equals to <strong>0.123456789</strong> before. After the code it turns into <strong>0.12</strong> only.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
