    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>To print a float up to 2 decimal places in Java:</p>\n<pre><code>    float f = (float)11/3;\n    System.out.print(String.format(&quot;%.2f&quot;,f));\n</code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>OUTPUT: 3.67</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>&gt; use <strong>%.3f</strong> for up to three decimal places.</em></p>\n"
