    "body" : "<pre><code>public String getDecimalNumber(String number) {\n        Double d=Double.parseDouble(number);\n        return String.format(&quot;%.5f&quot;, d);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Take care of <code>NumberFormatException</code> as well</p>\n"
